- Copy files

mkdir ~/tmp
mkdir ~/bin

cp .tmux.conf ~/
cp -r .tmux ~/
cp .vimrc ~/
cp -r .vim ~/
cp mycscope ~/bin/
cp .bash* ~/


- Reboot

- Install TPM 
git clone https://github.com/tmux-plugins/tpm ~/.tmux/plugins/tpm

- Open a TMUX session and do below to install tmux-resurrect

ctrl-a shift-I


- Install Tabular


mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
cd ~/.vim/bundle
git clone git://github.com/godlygeek/tabular.git


- Install vim-easy-plugin for alignment

Open vim and type :PlugInstall
